        "message": "=<html><body style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px;\">\n<h2 style=\"color: #c0392b;\">Health QA: Content Blocked</h2>\n<p>The Health QA agent blocked this week's content. It has NOT been published.</p>\n<p><strong>Issues found ({{ $json.payload.issues.length }}):</strong></p>\n<table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n  <tr style=\"background:#f5f5f5;\"><th style=\"padding:8px;text-align:left;\">Check</th><th style=\"padding:8px;text-align:left;\">Location</th><th style=\"padding:8px;text-align:left;\">Flagged Text</th><th style=\"padding:8px;text-align:left;\">Fix</th></tr>\n  {{ $json.payload.issues.map(i => '<tr><td style=\"padding:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">' + i.check + '</td><td style=\"padding:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">' + i.location + '</td><td style=\"padding:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-style:italic;\">' + i.flagged_text + '</td><td style=\"padding:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">' + i.fix_instruction + '</td></tr>').join('') }}\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin-top:20px;\">The Writer agent needs to fix these issues and resubmit.</p>\n<p><strong>Run ID:</strong> {{ $json.run_id }}</p>\n</body></html>",
        "options": {}
